reviews.text:
This one is something else. The shortbread, cookie bite, and butter base make for delicious buttery shortbread cookies. The Bounty adds in the chocolate and coconut. The simple genius move of adding in the toffee ice cream gives the caramel note that perfects the samoa cookie side, and enriches the vanilla ice cream. Honestly, and I freely admit it's the Samoa junkie in me, wishes there was a touch more chocolate, but that'd wreck the balance of this absolutely excellent treat. Vape your calories indeed!&#xD;
&#xD;
Nicely done all!

Absolutely love it, after only a one day steep and it’s  Creamy, buttery, chocolaty, biscuity, soft and chewy&#xD;
&#xD;
It’s a complex one but all the elements are there
